            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" data-id="jewish-quarter">
            <div class="save-btn" aria-label="save Jewish Quarter">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="label">Cultural</div>
            <h3>Jewish Quarter</h3>
            <p>
              Layers of history woven in architecture—explore synagogues, narrow streets, and quiet
              reflection points.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

